{
  "text": "I would just state that this card, being male, would indicate that as experience is gained the mind becomes the motivator or that which reaches or \"does\" more than the simple experiencer prior to the catalytic action. That is, there is a greater tendency for the mind to direct the mind/body/spirit complex, and other than that I would just ask if there is anything that we can do to make the instrument more comfortable or improve the contact? I am Ra. In the context of your penultimate query we would suggest that you ponder again the shape of the garment which the image wears. Such habiliment is not natural. The shape is significant and is so along the lines of your query. The support group cares well for the instrument. We would ask that care be taken as the instrument has been offered the gift of a distortion towards extreme cold by the fifth-density friend which greets you. Although you may be less than pleased with the accoutrements, may we say that all was as carefully prepared as each was able. More than that none can do. Therefore, we thank each for the careful alignments. All is well. We leave you, my friends, in the love and in the light of the One Glorious Infinite Creator. Go forth, then, rejoicing in the power and in the peace of the One. Adonai.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "I would just state that this card, being male, would indicate that as experience is gained the mind becomes the motivator or that which reaches or \"does\" more than the simple experiencer prior to the catalytic action.",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 217,
        "start": 3.16,
        "end": 58.224
      },
      {
        "segment": "That is, there is a greater tendency for the mind to direct the mind/body/spirit complex, and other than that I would just ask if there is anything that we can do to make the instrument more comfortable or improve the contact?",
        "start_offset": 218,
        "end_offset": 444,
        "start": 59.564,
        "end": 83.345
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 445,
        "end_offset": 453,
        "start": 83.565,
        "end": 86.105
      },
      {
        "segment": "In the context of your penultimate query we would suggest that you ponder again the shape of the garment which the image wears.",
        "start_offset": 454,
        "end_offset": 581,
        "start": 89.886,
        "end": 123.668
      },
      {
        "segment": "Such habiliment is not natural.",
        "start_offset": 582,
        "end_offset": 613,
        "start": 125.448,
        "end": 133.248
      },
      {
        "segment": "The shape is significant and is so along the lines of your query.",
        "start_offset": 614,
        "end_offset": 679,
        "start": 136.269,
        "end": 155.05
      },
      {
        "segment": "The support group cares well for the instrument.",
        "start_offset": 680,
        "end_offset": 728,
        "start": 163.55,
        "end": 173.351
      },
      {
        "segment": "We would ask that care be taken as the instrument has been offered the gift of a distortion towards extreme cold by the fifth-density friend which greets you.",
        "start_offset": 729,
        "end_offset": 887,
        "start": 177.511,
        "end": 212.993
      },
      {
        "segment": "Although you may be less than pleased with the accoutrements, may we say that all was as carefully prepared as each was able.",
        "start_offset": 888,
        "end_offset": 1013,
        "start": 216.974,
        "end": 257.476
      },
      {
        "segment": "More than that none can do.",
        "start_offset": 1014,
        "end_offset": 1041,
        "start": 260.336,
        "end": 264.777
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, we thank each for the careful alignments.",
        "start_offset": 1042,
        "end_offset": 1094,
        "start": 267.397,
        "end": 277.638
      },
      {
        "segment": "All is well.",
        "start_offset": 1095,
        "end_offset": 1107,
        "start": 277.658,
        "end": 280.718
      },
      {
        "segment": "We leave you, my friends, in the love and in the light of the One Glorious Infinite Creator.",
